  "name": "Hammer",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Taijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As part of the activation of this jutsu, you must be targeting a creature who can be targeted by a taijutsu with the Finisher keyword regardless of the range.</p><p>You bring your hands together, interlocking your fingers until your hands resemble a single bludgeoning device.</p><p>Make a melee taijutsu attack dealing your [Unarmed Damage] + 3d8 bludgeoning damage and the target must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save they gain +1 rank of concussed and Dazed</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d8.</p>",
